			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="- Load up GustavDev/SCL_Main_A&#xD;&#xA;- Either use &quot;goto 715 11 -109&quot; in ReCon and go to the last step or follow the next steps.&#xD;&#xA;- Go to the Colony Necromancer's Chamber (debugbook option)&#xD;&#xA;- Escape or kill the cage you get teleported into.&#xD;&#xA;- Kill combat.&#xD;&#xA;- Interact with S_COL_NecroLab_BasRelief_7f89f4d1-a6a9-4181-8563-d10f74444557&#xD;&#xA;- use &quot;oe COL_Vault_AutoSolve&quot; in debug to auto solve puzzle" />
